                    child: Padding(
                      padding: EdgeInsets.all(10),
                      child: Text(
                          'Admissions are open for the 2025 academic year. Apply now!'),
                    ),
                  ),
                  Card(
                    child: Padding(
                      padding: EdgeInsets.all(10),
                      child: Text(
                          'Upcoming placement drive by top MNCs next month.'),
                    ),
                  ),
